      <title>美联储理事可能不欢迎特朗普的意见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trump-appointee-possible-fed-chair-waller-doesn-t-want-political-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普希望白宫有权决定利率。被视为特朗普第二任期内美联储主席候选人的美联储理事强烈反对这一想法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trump-appointee-possible-fed-chair-waller-doesn-t-want-political-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>KBW 称 UniCredit 可能会在德国商业银行重复德国成本削减措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/unicredit-may-repeat-germany-cost-cuts-at-commerzbank-kbw-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KBW 分析师在一份报告中写道，UniCredit SpA 已在其现有的德国子公司证明其可以在该国削减成本，这对其针对德国商业银行的潜在计划来说是个好兆头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/unicredit-may-repeat-germany-cost-cuts-at-commerzbank-kbw-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:58:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非 OUTsurance 飙升至创纪录水平；计划发放特别赔款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/south-africa-s-outsurance-surges-to-record-plans-special-payout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非保险公司 OUTsurance Group Ltd. 宣布全年利润大幅增长并将派发特别股息，此后该公司股价飙升至历史新高。该公司在澳大利亚和爱尔兰均有业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/south-africa-s-outsurance-surges-to-record-plans-special-payout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:51:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一系列坏消息令德国投资者信心暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/german-investor-confidence-plummets-after-spate-of-bad-news</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有进一步迹象表明德国制造业巨头面临越来越不确定的未来，投资者对德国经济的信心跌至近一年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/german-investor-confidence-plummets-after-spate-of-bad-news</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:06:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
